== Khilaafaadka ==

=== Fadeexad dharka ===
Fadeexad maro-dhareedka ayaa dhacday intii lagu guda jiray dhacdadii ''[[Inkigayo]]'' ee Janaayo 29, 2012 taas oo Ryu ay si lama filaan ah u qaawisay naaska intii ay socotay qoob ka ciyaarka. Sawir-qaade ayaa ku wareegay onlayn iyada oo loo marayo marinnada warbaahinta Kuuriya. [[JoongAng Ilbo]] ayaa sheegay in barnaamijka uu si toos ah u tabinayay markii uu shilku dhacay.<ref>{{cite web|title=티아라 화영 노출·BAP 무대 함몰...'인기가요' 질타|url=http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=7235399|work=[[JoongAng Ilbo]]|access-date=9 October 2012|language=ko|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619171202/http://article.joinsmsn.com/news/article/article.asp?total_id=7235399|archive-date=19 June 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=티아라 화영 노출사고, SBS '인기가요' 제작진에 '불똥'|url=http://news.donga.com/3/all/20120130/43653437/4|work=[[The Dong-a Ilbo]]|access-date=9 October 2012|language=ko|date=2012-01-30}}</ref>  [[MBK Entertainment|Core Contents Media]] waxay soo saartay bayaan rasmi ah oo ku saabsan nipslip-ka: "Masraxa T-ara waxay ahayd mid si toos ah loo sameeyay, waxayna ahayd shil si toos ah loo tabinayay. Ma jirin wax dhibaato ah intii ay ku celcelinayeen [...].  Kahor xaqiiqda inay tahay qof caan ah, wali waa da 'yar, markaa waxaan rajaynaynaa in dadku ay xasuusan doonaan inay tahay gabadh yar."<ref name="soompi.com">{{cite web|title=Core Contents Media and "Inkigayo" PD Apologizes about Hwayoung's Incident|url=http://www.soompi.com/2012/01/30/core-contents-media-and-inkigayo-pd-apologizes-about-hwayoungs-accident/|work=[[soompi]]|access-date=5 June 2012}}</ref> SBS ayaa soo saartay qoraal raaligelin ah.<ref name="soompi.com" />

=== Xoogsheegashada iyo arrimaha sharciga ===
